title: Calc It v1.6
description:
Calc It is an addictive game that stimulates your brain and speed. Fun, challenging and competitive for people of all ages. Calc It will be your favorite pickup-and-play game.

A beautiful and addictive puzzle game with an emphasis on fast-paced action and beautiful graphics! Reach the goal number before the timer runs out and score extra points by getting combos and speed bonuses!

Features:

- Beautiful and colorful scenario.
- Exercise your brain while having fun. 
- Nice graphics, music and sound effects
- Never gets old.
- Secret bonuses.
